Contact Us & FAQ’s
Contact
Racetrack RV
330 innovation way
Daytona Beach FL 32124
(386)366-0096
Hours
Mon-Sun => 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM
For more information please call us at
(386)-366-0096
or email us at
info.racetrackrv@gmail.com
FAQ’s
Q. Are You close to Daytona International Speedway?
A. Yes, we are right across the street from the track just walk out our back gate and cross midway.
Q. Are you a full hookup campground?
A. No, We are water and electric sites only.
Q. Do you have a dump station?
A. No, we do not have a dump station, but there is a pump-out truck ($) that comes around every day.
Every three days you stay, you get one free pump-out.
Q. How big are your sites?
A. We have four different size sites: 50’x18′, 50’x27′, 70’x18′ and 100’x18′.
